# HotkeyFooter Demo - styled hotkey hint display
Source demos/settings.tape
Output demos/gifs/hotkey_footer.gif

Hide
Type "cargo run --example hotkey_footer_demo"
Enter
Sleep 5s
Show

# View default style (brackets, cyan)
Sleep 2s

# Switch to Minimal preset
Right
Sleep 2s

# Switch to Vim preset
Right
Sleep 2s

# Switch to Pipe separator
Right
Sleep 2s

# Switch to Centered alignment
Right
Sleep 2s

# Cycle back to default
Right
Sleep 2s

Type "q"
